Hello Richard & All,
I appreciate the response. We will complete the testing on Friday afternoon=
, as described below, and provide the laboratory results along with the cor=
responding reports as soon as we have them back.
It would assist us in completing the tests with efficiency if we could have=
 maximum insight, by having the following questions from my previous email =
answered prior:

To ensure effectual testing it would be beneficial if you could confirm the=
 following:

  *   That the chlorine was located in the laundry room downstairs at the t=
ime of the fire.
  *   The quantity of the chlorine that was in that room at the time of the=
 fire. 1 container ?
  *   Where there any other chemicals that were located in that same room, =
or anywhere else downstairs.

Many Thanks,
Grant.
[cid:image001.png@01DC3DE3.70C76AE0]
Grant Metson
Regional Manager - House Assessing
Phone 021 744 288
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street,
PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142

