Good afternoon Grant,

Thank you for your message, I have spoken with my client. We (Wynn Williams=
) will not attend the site visit at 2pm on Friday. It=E2=80=99s a site visi=
t for Tower to undertake its testing and evaluation, and there can be no us=
eful discussion about the policy response until the testing is complete and=
 reports in. On that basis, please send through all reports / background in=
formation / relevant correspondence from the site visit as soon as they are=
 available. At that point we will be in a position to determine whether any=
thing further is needed, or meet to discuss next steps/policy response.

Thanks and kind regards

