<body lang=3D"EN-US" link=3D"blue" vlink=3D"purple" style=3D"word-wrap:brea=
k-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Richard &amp;=
 All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I appreciate the re=
sponse. We will complete the testing on Friday afternoon, as described belo=
w, and provide the laboratory results along with the corresponding reports =
as soon as we have them back.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">It would assist us =
in completing the tests with efficiency if we could have maximum insight, b=
y having the following questions from my previous email answered prior:<o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">To ensure effect=
ual testing it would be beneficial if you could confirm the following:<o:p>=
</o:p></span></u></p>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0in" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l2 level1 =
lfo6"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">That the chlorine was located in the=
 laundry room downstairs at the time of the fire.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li=
 class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo=
6"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The quantity of the chlorine that was i=
n that room at the time of the fire. 1 container ?<o:p></o:p></span></li><l=
i class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l2 level1 lf=
o6"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Where there any
<u>other chemicals</u> that were located in that same room, or anywhere els=
e downstairs. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many Thanks,<o:p></=
o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant.<o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
