<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-=
family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Good aftern=
oon Grant,
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-=
family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;=
</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-=
family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Thank you f=
or your message, I have spoken with my client. We (Wynn Williams) will not =
attend the site visit at 2pm on Friday. It=E2=80=99s a site
 visit for Tower to undertake its testing and evaluation, and there can be =
no useful discussion about the policy response until the testing is complet=
e and reports in. On that basis, please send through all reports / backgrou=
nd information / relevant correspondence
 from the site visit as soon as they are available. At that point we will b=
e in a position to determine whether anything further is needed, or meet to=
 discuss next steps/policy response.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-=
family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;=
</o:p></span></p>
